    dc:description "Fig. 60. Scipopus (Phaeopterina) metallicus sp. nov. (SEMC). A. Head, J, anterolateral view, Mexico, holotype. B. Genital fork, ventral view, Mexico, paratype. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view, holotype. D. Male terminalia, lateral view, Mexico, paratype. E. Habitus, Mexico, holotype. Abbreviations: b = basiphallus; bdp = basal distiphallus; e = epandrium; h = hypandrium; p = phallapodeme; pb = phallic bulb." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10123417/files/figure.png" ;
